13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 10A O.S. 2021, Section 2-4-107, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 2-4-107. A. 1. The salary of the director and other
17 employees of the bureau and any detention home established pursuant
18 to Section 2-4-108 of this title shall be fixed by the judge of the
19 Juvenile Division, subject to the general administrative authority
20 of the county commissioners of the contracting county. The salary
21 of the director shall not exceed ninety percent (90%) of salaries of
22 county Class A officers.
